abstract: Jamaican sprinter Usain Bolt will compete at Diamond League meet June 13 on Randalls Island.
lead_paragraph: Bolt will run in New York for the first time since he set the world record there in the 100 meters in 2008.

headline.main: Usain Bolt Is Set for New York Race
